                     xml:lang="en">MS is a postcard.</p>
               </note>DEUTSCHE REICHSPOST</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">POSTKARTE<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
